snippet.title: Leisure Suit Larry - Wet Dreams Don't Dry (Trailer EN)
snippet.description:
Larry Laffer is back in time and will encounter a new adventure on November 7th 2018 on Steam and GoG for PC and MAC. The new gameplay trailer Leisure Suit Larry - Wet Dreams Don't Dry tells you what it's all about and what you can expect.

Pre-order now on Steam:https://store.steampowered.com/app/765870/Leisure_Suit_Larry__Wet_Dreams_Dont_Dry/

Pre-order now on GoG: https://www.gog.com/game/leisure_suit_larry_wet_dreams_dont_dry
